OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772780660
OL,3,CBritish couple sheltered in car park
OL,4,Cunder hotel before catching flight home
OL,6,FA couple who arrived back in the UK on
OL,7,Fthe first chartered flight from the
OL,8,FMiddle East said they sheltered in a
OL,9,Fcar park beneath their hotel in Dubai.
OL,11,FThousands of British nationals are
OL,12,Fstranded in the Middle East after US-
OL,13,FIsraeli strikes on Iran prompted
OL,14,Fretaliatory strikes across the region.
OL,16,FThe first Government chartered flight
OL,17,Ftook off from Muscat, the capital of
OL,18,FOman, at 1.36pm GMT on Thursday,
OL,19,Fhaving initially been scheduled for
OL,20,F7pm on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
