FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772780660
OL,3,CBritish couple sheltered in car park
OL,4,Cunder hotel before catching flight home
OL,6,FThe Titan Airways plane touched down
OL,7,Fat London Stansted just before 1am on
OL,8,FFriday, carrying mostly families with
OL,9,Fyoung children.
OL,11,FAmelia Reid and Samuel Sharp travelled
OL,12,Fto Dubai for a long weekend, arriving
OL,13,Flast Friday, and by Saturday evening
OL,14,Fthey were sheltering under their hotel.
OL,16,FThey had travelled for more than 40
OL,17,Fhours by the time they touched down at
OL,18,FStansted, where they were greeted by
OL,19,FMs Reid's parents and their dog Penny.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772780660
OL,3,CBritish couple sheltered in car park
OL,4,Cunder hotel before catching flight home
OL,6,FMr Sharp said: "Saturday we ended up
OL,7,Fsleeping in a car park in the basement
OL,8,Fof the hotel with about 100 other
OL,9,Fpeople, after the alarms went off on
OL,10,Four phones.
OL,12,F"Didn't get told if it was safe to go
OL,13,Fup or not, just went up for breakfast
OL,14,Fand I think we heard a massive bang
OL,15,Fafter that, so it's just on edge, on
OL,16,Fedge for four days.
OL,26,@nD@POUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
