OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772780660
OL,3,CBritish couple sheltered in car park
OL,4,Cunder hotel before catching flight home
OL,6,FMs Reid, who had been travelling in a
OL,7,Fwheelchair, said: "We left Dubai
OL,8,Fyesterday lunchtime, went straight to
OL,9,Fthe Oman border, and went on a coach
OL,10,Fall the way to Muscat airport in the
OL,11,Fhope we'd get on the Government plane."
OL,13,FShe explained that after arriving at
OL,14,FMuscat airport and boarding the
OL,15,Fchartered flight on Wednesday evening,
OL,16,Fthey were told they would not be
OL,17,Ftaking off because the pilot was out
OL,18,Fof hours.
OL,26,@oD@SOUsD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
