OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772780660
OL,3,CBritish couple sheltered in car park
OL,4,Cunder hotel before catching flight home
OL,6,FAnother man, who wished to remain
OL,7,Fnameless, described the "terrible"
OL,8,Fwait for the plane to take off on
OL,9,FWednesday evening, before the delay to
OL,10,FThursday afternoon.
OL,12,FHe, his wife and young child spent 36
OL,13,Fhours in Muscat airport, after fleeing
OL,14,FDubai last weekend.
OL,26,@oD@YOUoD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772780660
OL,3,CBritish couple sheltered in car park
OL,4,Cunder hotel before catching flight home
OL,6,FHe said: "To be honest, UAE (United
OL,7,FArab Emirates) government has been
OL,8,Fdoing very good with the interception
OL,9,F(of missiles) and making people safe,
OL,10,Fbut it's just that I thought it's not
OL,11,Fworth any of this, even if something
OL,12,Fminor happens, especially for the
OL,13,Ffamily, it's not good."
OL,15,FHe drove 300 miles from Dubai to Oman
OL,16,Fearlier this week.
OL,26,@nD@JOUuD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772780660
OL,3,CBritish couple sheltered in car park
OL,4,Cunder hotel before catching flight home
OL,6,FThe man continued: "I think today was
OL,7,Fbetter, but the day before was very
OL,8,Fterrible. We took almost four hours
OL,9,Ffor check-in. And then after that, we
OL,10,Fwere told we can't fly because pilot
OL,11,Fis on overtime, so we had to go back
OL,12,Fto the hotel."
OL,14,FMore than 140,000 Britons have
OL,15,Fregistered their presence in the
OL,16,FMiddle East with the Foreign Office
OL,17,Fand 4,000 have returned home.
OL,19,FMuscat has emerged as a key location
OL,20,Ffor people wanting to leave the Middle
OL,21,FEast.
OL,26,@nD@TOUtD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
