PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772780660
OL,3,CBritish couple sheltered in car park
OL,4,Cunder hotel before catching flight home
OL,6,FThe Foreign Office does not advise
OL,7,Fagainst travel to the area where the
OL,8,Fcapital's airport is located, unlike
OL,9,Fthe current advice for airports in
OL,10,FDubai, Abu Dhabi and Doha.
OL,12,FMuscat can be reached by road from
OL,13,Fboth Dubai and Abu Dhabi with journeys
OL,14,Fof about 300 miles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772780660
OL,3,CBritish couple sheltered in car park
OL,4,Cunder hotel before catching flight home
OL,6,FSir Keir revealed he had chaired a
OL,7,FCobra meeting on Thursday, and
OL,8,Facknowledged that people across the UK
OL,9,Fare "worried sick about their family
OL,10,Fand friends who are caught up" in a
OL,11,Fwar he said "could continue for some
OL,12,Ftime".
OL,14,FFazal Chowdhury, who described himself
OL,15,Fas a "risk averse kind of guy" also
OL,16,Ftouched down on the flight with his
OL,17,Fwife.
OL,19,FHe complimented the UK Government's
OL,20,Fwork despite the long delay.
OL,26,@qD@EOUrD@^O]sD@MOUtD@EO]wD@FOUwD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772780660
OL,3,CBritish couple sheltered in car park
OL,4,Cunder hotel before catching flight home
OL,6,FMr Chowdhury, who had lived in Dubai
OL,7,Ffor the last three years, said: "There
OL,8,Fwas a bit of room for improvement
OL,9,Fbecause there were some technical
OL,10,Fissues with the flight, so we were in
OL,11,Fthe airport for 20 hours, but I don't
OL,12,Fthink there's much to complain about.
OL,14,F"To be honest, they were all working
OL,15,Freally hard and they were all really
OL,16,Fsincere, the whole team there were
OL,17,Freally good.
OL,26,@oD@aOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772780660
OL,3,CBritish couple sheltered in car park
OL,4,Cunder hotel before catching flight home
OL,6,F"The ambassador came and explained
OL,7,Fwhat happened, she was really good.
OL,8,FWe're all here now, it was a bit of a
OL,9,Fshambles on the night when we thought
OL,10,Fwe were going to get on the flight and
OL,11,Fthen we were sort of trapped on buses
OL,12,Fand had to go back."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
